profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
Home Additions Builders Basement Renovation Kitchen Planning & Renovation General Contractors 

At Oborne Contracting we pride ourselves on customer service. We specialize in additions, kitchens, bathrooms, basements, and all other home renovation and remodeling needs. Our team is courteous, skilled, conscientious and determined to ensure each project is completed on time and on budget. Our longstanding trades are reliable professionals who are committed to their work and quality. We are confident that you will find at Oborne Contracting we conduct ourselves on a highly professional level, assuring your complete satisfaction is our key to success.Oborne Contracting Inc. has been servicing Toronto and surrounding area home owners for over 20 years. We specialize in custom home building, general contracting, home repairs, design and build, home remodeling and restoration, home additions and basement renovations. 
We take pride in attending to every detail of any project we take on, from the initial meeting with the discerning home owner until after the job is completed. After working with our professional staff you will understand why Oborne Contracting Inc. will be your first choice for all of your home upgrades, renovations and new constructions.

Each home remodeling project is unique in the level of complexity and requirements. This demands a level of experience to design a broad plan and turn any project into a functional and livable home upgrade, addition or custom design. We build our client’s trust by understanding their needs, budgets, time frames, while supervising every step of the construction process. No question is ever left unanswered.

profile:
For 35 years and counting, Tropical Insulation Inc., has been the best choice for blown in, loose fill cellulose insulation installations across Toronto, the GTA and Southern Ontario. Whether you are a Homeowner involved in remodeling, renovating or retrofitting your home, or an Industry Professional or Contractor looking for a reputable insulation contractor for your next project, we can deliver reliable and prompt service at a competitive price, using only the highest quality Canadian-manufactured cellulose insulation on the market today. 
With the cost of living skyrocketing, saving money by saving energy has never been more important. Heating and cooling costs can account for 50-70% of a home or building’s yearly energy expense. When installed correctly, insulation is the simplest and most cost-effective means to lower this energy use. Remember, sealing and ventilating your home correctly will not only keep you warm in winter but will also cool you down in the summer months… Insulation is the perfect four season solution to saving you money.
If you are working on a “Green Building” project, or consider environmental sustainability a factor in your decision-making when selecting an insulation installer, please contact us. We choose to install Climatizer Plus™ cellulose insulation for its superior thermal and acoustical performance as well as its environmental benefits. Climatizer Plus loose-fill cellulose is certified by UL’s ECOLOGO program; indicating that this product has undergone rigorous scientific testing, auditing, or both, to prove its compliance with stringent, third party, environmental performance standards and may help you contribute to LEED credit categories.   
Call us or “Get started today” on our website and allow us to provide you the information you need to make an informed choice for your home or building insulation needs.  We offer free in-home assessments and quotes.

profile:
Why choose The Renovators of Canada?  
 
For over the past 20 years our focus on customer experience has helped The Renovators of Canada grow to locations in Durham, Aurora, Stouffville, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, Hamilton, Guelph, Kitchener, Waterloo, Barrie, Oshawa, Oakville and Cambridge. 
 
Unique to the industry, The Renovators of Canada provides a 10 year warranty on all craftsmanship. This home renovation warranty protection was established to provide peace of mind as home and business owners contemplate renovating a personal or commercial space. 
 
T-ROC is a fully licensed and insured including WSIB. Other affiliations include memberships with the National Kitchen and Bath Association, CARAHS, Better Business Bureau.

WHY US?

*****

We are experienced, fully insured and fully licensed. We are built on a foundation of integrity; ECOCOR construction provides cost-effective development services centered on quality, performance and customer service and we respect people properties. We aim to exceed customer expectations by meeting deadlines, attending to every detail and providing the highest level of service; we make sure all of our extra material and disposals is recycled properly, we make sure we go out of our way to our client. We are proud of our completed projects, yet even prouder of the relationships we have built along the way through professionalism, honesty, and fairness.

*****

Your experience at ECOCOR is unique in that our process is solely customer focused. Relationships

profile: Welcome to Classic View Home additions Making Your House a Home The most important part of your home remodelling and renovations is you. Our main priority is taking your vision of your home and making it a reality by providing honest, trustworthy and reliable services. Your home improvements are made a positive experience by keeping a smile on your face and always being available to answer your questions. Classic View takes care to always add a personal touch! Consultation Our process begins by meeting and listening to your needs and wants. Through conversations, questions and photos, Classic View determines the total scope of work required for your remodelling or renovation. We believe in setting mutual expectations right from the start - ensuring you always know: *What we are doing *How much it will cost *What the final results will be Classic View will also help guide you when selecting plumbing fixtures, cabinetry, flooring, tiles and everything else through our wide network of trusted suppliers. Project Management We believe that a successful remodelling project is the result of a partnership between the client and the company. Classic View takes care of virtually everything from beginning to end - including architectural plans and all building permits. If preferred, you are welcome to also use your own architect for drawings. Here are a few of the things we do to ensure your project is managed effectively and delivered on time: *Detailed price and completion date estimate within three days from the first meeting. *No hidden costs or surprises – the budget is guaranteed! *You are provided a contract that includes the project timeline, payment schedule, detailed pricing, warranty details, proof of insurance and more. *By only managing a very small number of projections concurrently, Classic View ensures projects finished in a timely fashion. Promise: Focus and attention on your project is paramount. Classic View will ensure your project receives the attention it deserves. Superior Workmanship Superior workmanship is critical to ensure that your home improvements look as good years later as they did the day they were completed. Classic View’s trades people work as a team and are the best at what they do. We aim for perfection. Fact: Classic View has successfully passed every city inspection, never having had to rebuild any work on any project. Customer Service A Classic View project is successful when you are happy and thrilled with the end results. *Trust, reliability and honesty are the foundation of the service we provide. *We keep you involved at all times. *Through email and personalized web blogs we regularly communicate our work schedule,encourage communication and provide updates. *Every effort is made to educate our customers of all options and methods of construction throughout the project.
